Package: drone-surveillance
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.7), python3-venv, python3-pip
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Description: Drone Surveillance System
 A Python-based drone surveillance system that uses computer vision
 to detect fires and other objects of interest. The system integrates
 with DroneKit for drone control and GPS coordinate tracking.
